WEBVTT

00:09.426 --> 00:13.856
This is Dr. Frasier Crane. We'll be right back after this.

00:13.856 --> 00:19.414
OK, after this spot we're gonna come back in 15 seconds, you do a station ID and then toss it to the news.

00:19.414 --> 00:20.468
I'll count you down.

00:20.468 --> 00:21.771
That won't be necessary.

00:21.771 --> 00:23.986
I have a built in mental stopwatch.

00:23.986 --> 00:31.433
As a child playing "Hide and Go Seek"
I was the only one who didn't need to say, "One Hippopotamus Two Hippopotamus."

00:31.433 --> 00:35.199
Frasier, I've heard you.  You're always either talking into the news or running short.

00:35.199 --> 00:36.744
I am not!

00:36.744 --> 00:40.356
I'll bet you 20 bucks you blow this one.

00:40.356 --> 00:41.439
All right, you're on.

00:41.439 --> 00:44.431
No, you are.

00:46.580 --> 00:53.243
Hello, we're back.  This is Dr. Frasier Crane tuning in for our second hour on the "Dr. Frasier Crane Show."

00:53.243 --> 00:57.020
