00:57.020 --> 01:01.873
What will be next?  As always of course that's entirely up to you.

01:01.873 --> 01:07.306
So stick around ?the Doctor is in and he's listening.

01:07.306 --> 01:15.023
Ooh, this is KACL 780 AM...
This is nbc news..

