Ladies and Gentlemen.  I just spoke with our captain and we're having a little technical snag.

17:09.526 --> 17:14.555
So Flight 487 to Chicago will be delayed indefinitely.

17:14.555 --> 17:18.574
I missed you!
I missed you too!

17:18.574 --> 17:25.387
The minute that door closed I started praying for something bad to happen to your plane.

17:26.300 --> 17:29.905
It's just like fate ?like somebody's willing us to get together.

17:29.905 --> 17:31.689
I felt that way since the moment I met you.

17:31.689 --> 17:34.801
Me too.

17:34.801 --> 17:36.203
Why don't you come with me tonight?

17:36.203 --> 17:38.995
I gotta work.  I could come out next weekend.

17:38.995 --> 17:43.899
Oh, yeah.  Oh, great.
You know what, you can meet my twin sister.  She lives in Chicago.

17:43.899 --> 17:45.434
You've got a twin?
Yes.

17:45.434 --> 17:48.020
Wow.

17:48.020 --> 17:51.858
You know there's so much we don't know about each other.

17:51.858 --> 17:54.909
Well, ask me.  Ask me anything.

17:54.909 --> 17:58.825
Er... oh, I know.  What's your favourite colour?

17:58.825 --> 18:00.854
Blue.  What's yours?

18:00.854 --> 18:05.261
Arctic silver.  It's available on all the big BMW's.

18:05.261 --> 18:06.434
Where's your favorite city?

18:06.434 --> 18:08.052
Paris!  Museum?

18:08.052 --> 18:10.171
The Prada!  Musical?

18:10.171 --> 18:11.535
Candide!  Yours?

18:11.535 --> 18:14.762
Cats!

